        pieces, errors, oddities, counterfeits, unusual varieties, and related exonumia with useful
        collector or historical context.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="about-aside">
      <h3>Of Interest</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>NYC transportation tokens</li>
        <li>Unlisted and undocumented pieces</li>
