<section class="section">
  <div class="about-split">
    <div>
      <h2>Research and Corrections</h2>

      <p class="prose-width">
        Corrections, attributions, discoveries, provenance notes, and additional information are always
        appreciated. If you can help identify a token, clarify a variety, or improve a listing, please
        send the details along.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="about-aside">
      <h3>Helpful Details</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Clear photos of both sides</li>
        <li>Diameter, material, or weight</li>
        <li>Catalog references/attributions</li>
        <li>Discovery or ownership history</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

